(255, 1, '2024-07-22 18:31:01', '2024-07-22 18:31:01', '&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"mb-10 leading-loose\">Duet – Pleated Insect Net with Honeycomb Blackout is a dual purpose mosquito net cum window covering (2 in 1). Product launched by Insect Shield in Indian market. Honeycomb Blackout is lined with aluminium foil making excellent blackout blind &amp; insulator of heat. The dual purpose product is used in bedroom windows, home theatre windows, children nursery windows, hospital windows &amp; study windows. Duet – Pleated Insect Net / Honeycomb blackout saves precious space in apartments.</p>\r\n<p class=\"mb-10 leading-loose\">It is also the only window covering in India which ensures complete blackout and also saves electricity expenses. Honeycomb non-woven fabric is of the best quality and is waterproof but it should not be installed in windows which are exposed to rainfall. Cleaning has to be done either using a feather brush or a soft hand brush or a vacuum cleaner. Cleaning should never be done by scrubbing using soap &amp; water. Duet – Pleated Insect net is a very useful product if it is used with precautions as advised by company.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"my-8\">\r\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-16 py-12 text-center mb-3 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-light\">\r\n<div class=\"text-primary\"></div>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-lg font-medium my-2\">Quality We Ensure</h4>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm text-black/60\">Insect Shield team has the vision of being the best in all aspects of production</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-16 py-12 text-center mb-3 bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-light\">\r\n<div class=\"text-primary\"></div>\r\n<h4 class=\"text-lg font-medium my-2\">Technically Qualified Team</h4>\r\n<p class=\"text-sm text-black/60\">Training &amp; technical skills coupled with quality SOP makes Insect Shield team</p>\r\n\r\n</